1. How to start the app:
    a. in a new Linux terminal:
        docker-compose rm && docker-compose up
        (and wait for "database ready to accept connections")

    b. In another new Linux terminal: npm run start-dev-server

2. How to test the app:
    npm run test

3. How to run a single test:
    jest --config jest.unit.config.js $MY_FIRST_FAILING_TEST_PATH"